data.value:
Manual:
1. Load a Sudoku template. It has to be a .txt-file. In every single line has to be exactly 1 number. 0 means "this is a space". Sort the numbers by the lines (horizontal).
2. OPTIONAL - If you have a save file, load it now.
3. Play! Click on the field you want to edit and afterwards a number. If you think you solved it, press "Check". To save, use the saving function.
---------------------------------
Button colors: Green - everything worked Orange/Red - error/you did a mistake
